---
title: Parmesan-Crusted Chicken with Roasted Sweet Potato, Cranberry, and Arugula Salad
description: Everything tastes better when cheese is involved, and chicken is no exception. In this recipe, melted Parmesan forms a crispy and super simple crust. We would say it’s the star of the show, but the combination of roasted sweet potatoes, peppery arugula, and tart cranberries is hard to beat.
